    excerpt: 'Discover how safe messaging apps for kids go beyond chat to teach crucial digital etiquette, foster positive online friendships, and build responsible communication skills.',
    metaDescription: 'Discover how safe messaging apps for kids go beyond chat to teach crucial digital etiquette, foster positive online friendships, and build responsible communication skills.',
