    title: 'Online Gaming Safety: Parental Controls, Settings & Digital Boundaries',
    category: 'Online Safety',
    excerpt: 'Empower your family with our guide to online gaming safety. Learn essential parental controls, privacy settings, and how to set digital boundaries for a secure gaming experience.',
    metaDescription: 'Empower your family with our guide to online gaming safety. Learn essential parental controls, privacy settings, and how to set digital boundaries for a secure gaming experience.',
    readTime: 11,
    date: 'April 2026',
