    category: 'Online Safety',
    excerpt: 'Learn how AI and deepfake technology are being used by online predators. Essential guide for parents and educators to understand and counter these new threats.',
    metaDescription: 'Learn how AI and deepfake technology are being used by online predators. Essential guide for parents and educators to understand and counter these new threats.',
